  <div class="content">
    <h2>What is a Digital Footprint?</h2>
    <p>
      A digital footprint is the trail of data you leave behind when you use the internet.
      This includes your social media activity, emails, browsing history, app usage, and even deleted content.
    </p>
    <img src="https://www.cyber.gov.au/sites/default/files/styles/square_large/public/2020-07/digital-footprint.jpg" alt="Digital Footprint">

    <h2>Why It Matters</h2>
    <p>
      Your digital footprint can shape how others see you ‚Äî including schools, employers, and even cybercriminals.
      Once something is online, it's often there forever. Be cautious, thoughtful, and proactive.
    </p>

    <h2>Tips for Safe Internet Use</h2>
